    &lt;span class=&#34;token keyword&#34;&gt;this&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;token punctuation&#34;&gt;.&lt;/span&gt;_vnode &lt;span class=&#34;token operator&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; newVnode&lt;span class=&#34;token punctuation&#34;&gt;;&lt;/span&gt;
